        * irdp_{interface,main}.c: lists typedef removal cleanup.        
          update some list loops to LIST_LOOP. some miscellaneous style
          and indent fixups.
          (no_ip_irdp_address_preference_cmd) Fix delete of referenced node    
          in loop.
