	  field correctly. Add NEXTHOP_TYPE_IPV6_IFNAME for v6.
	  Conditionally set ZAPI_MESSAGE_METRIC flag - only for adds.
	  (zsend_ipv4_add) cruft, deleted.
	  (zsend_ipv4_delete) ditto.
